text: He Ying is an archer from China. She was born on 17 April 1977 in Siping. Ying competed at the 1996 Summer Olympics, 2000 Summer Olympics, and the 2004 Summer Olympics and won two medals.He YingYing HE == References == Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese archers Category:Olympic silver medalists for China
